phrases: I still do not get it.
Akagi, why did you decide to go out with me?
Ryoko-chan, you are calling me Ma-kun, not Akagi.
I am not answering your question unless you call me Ma-kun.
Seriously, we were talking about something important!
You knew I was going to do that.
What did you even see in me anyway?!
Dammit, we were in the middle of something serious!
You knew I was going to do that.
What do I like about you?
So my personality does not matter, does it?!
You have a cute face, though.
You do not care about what is on the inside at all?
Then what if you found someone cuter than me?
You have got plenty of things going for you.
That is all you care about!
You do not care about who I am, do you?!
I never said that, did I?
I think I do care about what is on the inside.
What is so good about me, then?
And you are a pain in the ass when you sulk like that.
Then why do not we break up already?!
Sure, you have got a lot of problems, but...
I do not want to hear it!
Y-You just like my boobs or some shit, right?
If you are happy, you can show it, you know.
You are so cute, you make me want to bully you.
Then tell me you like me again.
You do not want me to tell you I love you?
Fine, tell me you love me.
Just hurry up and say it.
Things got good with my boyfriend the other day.
But we ended up not doing anything.
Even dramas get special effects these days.
Neither of us has been able to make a move since then.
It is like we have been avoiding that kind of stuff.
I wonder if he is embarrassed that he got cockblocked.
It did not bother me, though.
I would not mind him being a bit more aggressive.
Then again, I would feel weird about bringing it up.
So have you seen it, Kana?
What were we talking about again?
We said we would get our comedy ideas from dramas because bang was getting old, remember?
So let us try me as the detective and you as the suspect.
Wait, I have never seen that show.
I will just go with the flow.
Honestly, I do not care about comedy ideas right now.
You have let your guard down!
Did he try to kiss me just now?
Do not tell me he is going to do it via skit.
No, no, no, you cannot be serious.
All right, I will be an alien next!
And you are the FBI agent this time.
YOU-Uh, all right, I will try.
Assuming he was trying to kiss me, this set up can only mean...
Stay back, or I will shoot!
This bit does not have a punch line.
We need to come up with something.
I heard you like movies, so if you are up for it...
Okay, see you tomorrow at the theater!
Let me guess, you were thinking about tomorrow.
Do Not Know what you are talking about...
We have plans to see a movie tomorrow, remember?
I have been so excited about it, I could not focus on the test.
Do not tell me you have forgotten.
We are supposed to watch Magic Shin-chan.
I never miss a movie in that series.
C-Can we do that the day after tomorrow?
It better not be a jezebel.
Such vile pigs deserve not to bask in the youth of we whom they deem gross!
I was invited by a guy friend, actually.
Oh, you have friends besides me?
He texted that we should catch up
Then I, Motoyama Tomomichi, shall yield to your previous engagement.
We are nothing if not repulsive.
Thus, the bonds of our friendships are our greatest treasure.
Do kindly introduce me to your friend someday.
I shall watch the movie by myself.
You are such a good man, Motoyama-kun.
And yet I lie just to spend time with a girl.
Okay, see you tomorrow at the theater!
I do not need a woman!
I do not have another friend.
My phonebook is only your number and my parents', and in fact
Well done, confiding in me a shameful truth.
I have never had the pleasure of having a soulmate.
Do what you must do tomorrow, Yamane-dono.
I shall not pry further, if you are inclined to hide it so.
We are friends, I will tell you.
Although, it is just that a girl I know asked me to watch a movie with her.
We actually had lunch together before,
but we did not really hit it off, so I do not know why she is inviting me again.
You lied to keep a woman hidden from me?
But I cannot go with you tomorrow
I implore you to choose her!
It warrants no mention that I despise women.
I would like nothing more than to render blind
those eyes with which they gaze upon me as though I am foul.
Just how could I possibly find fault in so pure a maiden
that she would call upon as repugnant a man as Yamane-dono?
Have the two of you entered into a relationship?
I mean, even that is presumptuous of me.
I do not even know what she is thinking, really.
I see, that is a platonic relationship.
Would you like to come with us?
I am sure she is going to bring her friends.
If you do not mind hanging out with girls.
Any friend of yours is perfectly acceptable to me.
A lot of people come to me for dating advice.
But I have never been in a relationship.
Sorry, but I do not care to talk to girls from above.
Why was he in the tree?
Were you helping a kitten stuck in the tree?
Nah, I just felt like climbing the tree.
So, what is on your mind?
You just had the same troubled look on your face as that kitty.
What is up with this guy, calling me a cute little kitty?
You do not think I am a dating master, do you?
Do you think you are cool or something?
There is nothing cool about a man who is made more girls cry than smile.
Oh dear, I would better stop calling myself the dating master,
or the dating gods will smite me.
If I am good enough for you.
I cannot do that, my kitten.
Fall for me, and you will get burnt.
No one can hold me down.
Come on, help me like you helped that kitty!
It is the spaghetti I had for lunch.
It is all because I was being stupid.
It is a prince's job to save a kitten in distress.
Do not put yourself in danger anymore.
Next time: It is All the Fever's Fault.
It is All the Fever's Fault
